                </div>
                <p>Under the hood, the Elroq is expected to deliver a robust performance with an impressive electric range of up to 300 miles per charge. Fast-charging capabilities allow for quick power-ups, making long journeys more convenient. The SUV also incorporates advanced safety features such as adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assist, and a comprehensive suite of driver-assist technologies, prioritizing safety for all occupants.</p>
                <p>With a variety of trim options available, including all-wheel drive configurations, the Elroq is designed to cater to diverse customer needs. As it prepares to make its debut, the Elroq is set to elevate Skoda's presence in the growing electric vehicle market.</p>
                <h3 class="subheading">Key Features</h3>
